        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is Machined?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Machined is an AI-powered SEO platform built around automated content clusters. Enter a seed keyword and it discovers related keywords, groups them into topic clusters, generates 30+ interlinked articles, and publishes them to WordPress or Webflow in under two hours.</p></div></div></div>
